{
  "stem": "4760.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[COUGHS] And then, when we got in there, we all-- and one thing about the Germans, they didn't want-- wanted to make sure you're always clean.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They adloused-- you know, they took your-- your clothes off, and put it in a cleaning process, like a cleaning machine, and cleaned everything, so that you had nothing to carry with you, lice, or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But before they did-- when they did that, they had us take off all our-- all our clothes and just left us in underpants.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before I left [COUGHS] my mother, my mother had sewed money and the addresses from all our relatives from-- from the United States in my pants, here in the-- in the band, you know?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the band.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[COUGHS] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- so I-- I was getting worried.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What will happen if I leave that money and the addresses in the pants?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what will happen to them?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had tried with my teeth to open it up-- the-- the-- the thread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And opened up the thread, and took out the money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I took out the addresses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the first thing I did with the addresses, I ripped them in 100 pieces and swallowed them, because the Germans were known that they can put paper together and find out what's behind it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How did you know that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "How did you know all that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You get to know all these things fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With some of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With some of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they all said, be careful with-- with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't have anything on you what could lead to something else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's why I took the papers, ripped them apart, and swallowed them.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
